The paper deals with security and privacy issues in Mobile Edge Computing (MEC) environments, which are related to cryptography, network security, distributed computing, and software engineering. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
